data.description: Nestled in the evergreens of Magalia, this property has tons of private forest views. Sit and enjoy a cup of coffee on your back covered patio with Tech decking and listen to the pine trees sing, the birds chirping. This home also features a semi-formal entry, large living room with tall vaulted ceiling, and sky lights for great natural lighting, gas fireplace for those cold winters, ceiling fan, elevated views of the rear yard. Beautiful kitchen with exquisite granite counters, eating bar area, abundant cabinetry, recessed lighting, formal dining area open to the kitchen. The large and inviting master bedroom offers a walk-in closet, sliding door to the back deck , the master bath flows from the master bedroom and offers a vanity/sink dressing area and private water closet with gorgeous walk-in tile shower. This home also features 2 guest rooms, 1 full bath and 1/2 bath, lots of storage closets, with a large 2-car extra deep garage and a large downstairs bonus living room with a slider going out to the backyard.
